     date | venue | city | state | tour | type | artists | image | friends | league | note
     · date    YYYY-MM-DD
     · type    Concert / Festival / Stand-Up / Football (drives the top-level category tab)
     · artists semicolons separate multiple acts (or teams, for football)
     · image   optional override for the headliner (row's first artist/team).
     · friends optional semicolon-separated list of who you went with.
               Photos live at people/<slug>.jpg; friends without a photo show initials.
     · league  Football rows only: NCAAF or NFL. Renders the league badge in place of
